# The frontend calls /api/ask-assistant and /api/maintenance-history via
# Vercel serverless functions — no VITE_API_URL needed.
#
# Set the following in your Vercel project environment variables
# (or locally in a .env.local file for the API functions):
#
# GOOGLE_API_KEY=<your-google-ai-studio-api-key>
#
# Get a free API key at https://aistudio.google.com/app/apikey
